#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.74"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.74:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.74:0.2"
msgid "8. Ākaṅkhavagga"
msgstr "8. If You Want"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.74:0.3"
msgid "74. Vaḍḍhisutta"
msgstr "74. Growth"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.137"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.74:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Dasahi, bhikkhave, vaḍḍhīhi vaḍḍhamāno ariyasāvako ariyāya vaḍḍhiyā "
"vaḍḍhati, sārādāyī ca hoti varādāyī kāyassa."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a noble disciple who grows in ten ways grows nobly, taking on "
"what is essential and excellent in this life."

msgctxt "an10.74:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi dasahi?"
msgstr "What ten?"

msgctxt "an10.74:1.3"
msgid ""
"Khettavatthūhi vaḍḍhati, dhanadhaññena vaḍḍhati, puttadārehi vaḍḍhati, "
"dāsakammakaraporisehi vaḍḍhati, catuppadehi vaḍḍhati, saddhāya vaḍḍhati, "
"sīlena vaḍḍhati, sutena vaḍḍhati, cāgena vaḍḍhati, paññāya vaḍḍhati—"
msgstr ""
"He grows in fields and lands, money and grain, wives and children, in "
"bondservants, workers, and staff, and in livestock. And he grows in faith, "
"ethics, learning, generosity, and wisdom."

msgctxt "an10.74:1.4"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, bhikkhave, dasahi vaḍḍhīhi vaḍḍhamāno ariyasāvako ariyāya "
"vaḍḍhiyā vaḍḍhati, sārādāyī ca hoti varādāyī kāyassāti."
msgstr ""
"A noble disciple who grows in ten ways grows nobly, taking on what is "
"essential and excellent in this life."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.74:2.1"
msgid "Dhanena dhaññena ca yodha vaḍḍhati,"
msgstr "Someone who grows in money and grain,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.74:2.2"
msgid "Puttehi dārehi catuppadehi ca;"
msgstr "in wives, children, and livestock,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.74:2.3"
msgid "Sa bhogavā hoti yasassi pūjito,"
msgstr "is wealthy, famous, and respected"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.74:2.4"
msgid "Ñātīhi mittehi athopi rājubhi."
msgstr "by relatives and friends, and even by royals."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an10.74:3.1"
msgid "Saddhāya sīlena ca yodha vaḍḍhati,"
msgstr "When someone grows in faith and ethics,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.74:3.2"
msgid "Paññāya cāgena sutena cūbhayaṃ;"
msgstr "wisdom, and both generosity and learning—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.74:3.3"
msgid "So tādiso sappuriso vicakkhaṇo,"
msgstr "a good man such as he sees clearly,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.74:3.4"
msgid "Diṭṭheva dhamme ubhayena vaḍḍhatī”ti."
msgstr "and in the present life he grows in both ways.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.74:3.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
